{"tid":1538523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地唔撚係諗住撤回就收貨下話！？","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:26.000Z","uid":228205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca59992ad8876ffce8d9dac588c93ee6535e08f2","tid":1538523,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"先唔講呢家只係傳話會撤回，就算係真都好<br />\n之前咁多烈士義士呢？你哋當佢哋condom牙？<br />\n<br />\n721元朗，831太子，805荃灣等多不勝數嘅克警例子呢？<br />\n咁就收貨對唔對得住死左嘅兄弟，重傷訓緊院嘅兄弟，上緊庭受審嘅兄弟呀？<br />\n<br />\n你哋老細哪你做野，你只做一樣，佢哋會唔會收貨呀？<br />\n<br />\n今次撤回左，過2年咪又再推過，你哋唔撚係信佢講野下話？<br />\n<br />\n今次一定要做到底，唔好再退再縮<br />\n預定行程不變！繼續塞，繼續罷，繼續行！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vw5oW5Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVw5oW5Y.png&h=0acc959a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"673c80091ad8200c5afccf23fbd03cc3da28677b","tid":1538523,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"3c6a242d6c468b87e707f0611997b2777f5e2040","tid":1538523,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"［幫手推］隔離熱門po話撤回條例會令下次遊行失去一大班和理非喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e99a569de3b080fe91fd1866465763e2bb7cb809","tid":1538523,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"d78295c1cc0b88371dcc5a96e9f0e139b4b62f8b","tid":1538523,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"2d682ef22e356b57041bae562e9c4627580f801d","tid":1538523,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"時代革命<br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"7c9695c